translations: n.麻醉医生，麻醉医师（等于 anesthetist）

phrs.translation: 出版商, 澳大利亚麻醉学会

sentences.sentence: This report describes an ethnographic study of document use by anaesthetists.
sentences.translation: 这是一份以人类学的方式，描绘在麻醉医疗中的文件使用现象的研究。

sentences.sentence: Most anaesthetists were not physicians (accredited anaesthetist per 100 000 population: 1.1).
sentences.translation: 大多数麻醉师并不是医师(每10万人中合格的麻醉师的比例为1.1)。

sentences.sentence: In-theatre training of anaesthetists in a teaching hospital: has it changed over 10 years?
sentences.translation: 教学医院手术室麻醉师培训在过去十年有变化吗？
